title: Chevaleresk
overview: Chevaleresk, the lifestyles program deepened in male style, is back. After the first season, Måns Zelmerlöw and Alexander Wiberg were nominated by the viewers of the TV award Kristallen as "Best Man Program Manager of the Year". Then through the series they had portrayed the modern gentleman. Now they are heading for a roadtrip in Sweden and Europe to explore typical Chevalar activities.
